    Machine Learning






            Music Genre Recognition
             Developed this project using Deep Neural Network with Keras API. This tool is
              capable of predicting the genre of any music by analyzing its spectrogram and then training the
              Keras
              model built using these spectrograms. Flask web framework is used to create an endpoint to this
              model.

            Check It Out





            Research Internship at IIT
            Worked on the problem of activity recognition from the videos using a Long-Term
              Recurrent Convolutional network (LRCN) and Capsule network (CapsNet).
              Proposed a new model called Long-Term Recurrent Convolutional network and Capsule network for
              activity recognition (LRCaps).












    Blockchain







            Blockchain Hackathon

              Participated in 48 hour Hackathon team event organized by Govt of Karnataka, where we developed the
              solution to challenge a problem called Real-time record maintenance using Blockchain.

            Check It Out






